sardar ( hindi : सरदार ) is a 1993 indian biopic on sardar vallabhbhai patel , one of india 's greatest freedom fighters , directed by ketan mehta and written by noted playwright vijay tendulkar . the film was screened retrospective on august 12 , 2016 at the independence day film festival jointly presented by the indian directorate of film festivals and ministry of defense , commemorating 70th indian independence day .